title: HANGAR 18 ( Invasion Force) 1980 Sci Fi Movie Robert Vaughn Gary Collins

sources.title: Hangar 18 Invasion Force 1980 Full Sci Fi Movie Robert Vaughn Gary Collins
sources.description: Shortly after the launch of a satellite from a space shuttle the satellite collides with an UFO in front of the crew's eyes. Because of an election campaign some politicians try to hide the crashed UFO -- inside hangar 18. Stars Robert Vaughn, Gary Collins, James Hampton
